
  Major changes between "nagios-plugins-filesystems" versions 1 and 2

* New module check_ifmount.c
* check_readonlyfs: new option -a|--all
* New header file 'common.h' containing stuff needed by all plugins.
* Porting on OpenBSD.
* Porting on AIX 6.1 with gcc.
* Update package documentation.

======================================================================

  Major changes between "nagios-plugins-filesystems" versions 0 and 1

* Add some documentation.
* Porting to Solaris and OpenIndiana 5.11 with gcc.
* Module 'check_readonlyfs' for Linux.

======================================================================
